#

Air Fryer Tofu and Vegetable Stir-Fry

35 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AsianAmerican

Course:

Main DishVegetarian

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuickAir Fryer

Description

A quick and healthy stir-fry featuring crispy tofu and colorful vegetables, all made in an air fryer!

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 14 oz
  • bell peppers (mixed colors): 2
  • broccoli florets: 1 cup
  • soy sauce: 3 tbsp
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
